Feature: First-time visitor navigates the EPAM website

Scenario: First-time visitor accesses the homepage
Given I am a first-time visitor
When I access the EPAM homepage
Then I should see clear information about who EPAM is
And I should see information about the services they offer
And I should see information about how they stand out
And I should see opportunities for partnerships

Scenario: First-time visitor navigates to the services page
Given I am a first-time visitor
When I navigate to the services page
Then I should see detailed information about the services EPAM offers

Scenario: First-time visitor navigates to the contact page
Given I am a first-time visitor
When I navigate to the contact page
Then I should see clear instructions on how to contact EPAM

Scenario: First-time visitor navigates to the case studies page
Given I am a first-time visitor
When I navigate to the case studies page
Then I should see relevant case studies

Scenario: First-time visitor navigates to the careers page
Given I am a first-time visitor
When I navigate to the careers page
Then I should see information about job opportunities
And I should see instructions on how to apply for a role

